<h2 id="using-textarea">Using textarea</h2>

<p>The textarea element enables users to input multiple lines of text.</p>

<p>It should be used for when users need to input information that is longer than a single line. For example, leaving feedback or providing supporting information in a form.</p>

<p>It shouldnâ€™t be used for single answer inputs, such as email address or National Insurance number.</p>

<p>Before using the textarea element, see if itâ€™s better to ask closed questions using <a href="multiple-choice">multiple choice</a> or <a href="inputs">inputs</a></p>

<p>Textarea is sometimes used as part of the <a href="/docs/core/components/form">form component</a></p>
